        <updateDate>2006-11-28T17:35:40Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[Constitutional Amendment - Prohibits a Federal judge of an inferior court from holding office, except with the consent of the Senate, for more than ten years after the judge took office, the Senate last consented to the judge's continuance in office, or this article is ratified, whichever occurs last.]]></text>
      </summary>
